We want beautiful babies,
not ones with brown faces.

29
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:37,840
Never, never, never, I say!
For the Ku Klux Klan is here to stay.

30
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:46,000
The Ku Klux Klan are better with lynches
than with lyrics.

31
00:08:46,160 --> 00:08:50,680
