37
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:10,640
Kennedy boy, now I see.

38
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:15,960
No, I do not think that you do.
Let us get this straight:

39
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:19,760
I have not had a pimple in years,
I shave every morning, -

40
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:24,680
- I even go to the bathroom by myself,
so you can quit this boss stuff.

41
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:27,840
I am in charge
